title: California Girls (Eclipse)
description:
The Eclipse Comics Upload Project lowers its head and charges ahead with 'California Girls' by Trina Robbins.

Info is scarce on this one but the Grand Comics Database files this under the double-genre of 'teen' and 'fashion'. Regardless, the artwork is simple and beautiful, accomplishing a lot with few lines and NO cross-hatching!!!!

The series ran for 8 issues and all are included here. Thanks to Trina and the scanners! Get it, seed it!
